RES0070,"D: What brought you in today?

P: Yeah absolutely. I have had this awful, awful headache for the past, two days I wanna say, its horrible.

D: OK, has the headache, uhm, stayed the same, gotten worse, gotten any better?

P: It's only gotten worse over the past two days.

